    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1963-07-23T04:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1963-07-23T04:00:00-05:00" n="342"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d342">
                <head>342. Telegram From the <gloss type="from">Embassy in the Soviet Union</gloss>
                    to the <gloss type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                    <note n="0" type="source" xml:id="d342fn0">Source: Department of State, Central
                        Files, DEF 18-3 <gloss target="#t_USSR1">USSR</gloss> (MO). Secret. Received
                        at 8:50 a.m.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Moscow</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1963-07-23T12:00:00+03:00">July 23, 1963, noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>277. From <persName corresp="#p_HWA2">Harriman</persName>. It is becoming crystal
                    clear that Soviets have as objective as described in Embtel 195<note n="1"
                        xml:id="d342fn1">
                        <ref target="#d331">Document 331</ref>.</note> attempt to isolate <gloss
                        target="#t_CHICOM1">ChiCom</gloss>s. Therefore, they place maximum
                    importance on France’s adherence to test ban treaty. Also they will press all
                    other countries to adhere. They want pressure to appear to come on <gloss
                        target="#t_CHICOM1">ChiCom</gloss>s from other countries, particularly the
                    underdeveloped, and therefore insisted on avoiding language in withdrawal clause
                    which would appear as pressure on China directly by them. This primary objective
                    will affect other positions they will take. In addition, atmosphere of relaxing
                    of tensions in Europe will have double purpose of showing value of coexistence
                    policies and avoiding battling on two fronts at same time.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_KFD1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Kohler</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
